ate with any homegrown systems they may have. This is a differentiator between&nbsp;<span class=\"highlight\" id=\"0.35874112455822904\" name=\"searchHitInReadingPane\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 238, 148);\">OverWatchID</span>&nbsp;and our competitors and eases sales conversations about converting from legacy systems at the client site to a full-blown&nbsp;<span class=\"highlight\" id=\"0.5523546480377941\" name=\"searchHitInReadingPane\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 238, 148);\">OverWatchID</span>implementation.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px;\">The team has also completed several User and Gateway Agent upgrades. These include a streamlined auto-update process, ability to access logs if the need to troubleshoot the agent ever arises, and the ability to route traffic through the agents. This will allow&nbsp;<span class=\"highlight\" id=\"0.8112451587383209\" name=\"searchHitInReadingPane\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 238, 148);\">OverWatchID</span>&nbsp;to support our Identity and Access Management (IAM) implementations and access clients LDAP/AD without having to expose those environments to the Internet. The team has also expanded Cloud Access Security Brokering (CASB) capabilities by building access capabilities to several new WebUI connections that our clients have requested.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px;\">In the near term, the team will focus efforts on furthering our IAM capabilities, expanding Multi-Factor Authentication (MFA) capabilities to include a Web SDK, and supporting the rollout latest updates to the&nbsp;<span class=\"highlight\" id=\"0.7421831504930549\" name=\"searchHitInReadingPane\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 238, 148);\">OverWatchID</span>&nbsp;Mobile App and Windows Credential Provider.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px;\"><b style=\"color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px;\">STAFFING &amp; TEAM:&nbsp;</b><br></p></div><div class=\"x_update-html-section\" style=\"color: rgb(74, 75, 77); font-family: Whitney, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px;\">&nbsp;The team is pleased to have two new resources join our Philippines team. Mac Valmore, a mobile application developer, and Ross Castroverde, a developer with expertise in python, have made an immediate impact. Mac will be leading enhancements to the IOS and Android versions of the mobile application, while Ross will continue to enhance the&nbsp;<span class=\"highlight\" id=\"0.3676642834184327\" name=\"searchHitInReadingPane\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 238, 148);\">OverWatchID</span>&nbsp;User and Gateway Agent.&nbsp;<br style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px;\">This past month&nbsp;<span class=\"highlight\" id=\"0.12231713421945423\" name=\"searchHitInReadingPane\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 238, 148);\">OverWatchID</span>&nbsp;decided to part ways with a single resource. This was not an easy decision, but we feel it was in the best interest of the team to move in a different direction.&nbsp;</p></div>'),(41,11,'2018-02-05','<p><a href=\"http://www.nibletz.com/events/sxswedu/bitsbox\" target=\"_blank\">SXSWedu Preview: Kids Can Easily Code Apps With Bitsbox</a></p><p><a href=\"http://fox17online.com/2018/02/25/grps-teacher-leads-the-way-with-innovation-classroom/\" target=\"_blank\">GRPS teacher leads the way with ‘Innovation Classroom’</a><br><br></p>');
